title: Andrei Ryabykh (footballer, born 1982)
text:
Andrei Mitrofanovich Ryabykh (; born 16 May 1982) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> player.
He represented Russia at the <a href="1999%20UEFA%20European%20Under-16%20Championship">1999 UEFA European Under-16 Championship</a>.
